captions.text:
Ooh, yay!
I love Geometry Dash.
I have it on my phone.
I play this on my iPad.
It's one of my favorite games.

You have to pass through levels 
by not hitting certain objects.

You have to tap to jump 
over the little obstacle courses

So I have to wait 
until the perfect moment...
It's like Flappy Bird all over again.
I mean, I think I'm gonna set a record.

Oh my gosh!
Oh my gosh.
I'm getting better and I got pretty far...
It's so frustrating, but it's so fun!
Why is this even fun though?

Oh my god!
Oh my god!

I'm trying to jump over 
all these little hurdles.
I feel like this is gonna be very hard.

I got to the part that I wanted 
to get over, but I died.

I got over it!
I got over it.

I got past it.
I got past it. Yeah.

I haven't played this game in a while,
so I'm kind of bad at it.
I've played this before and I completed it.

I don't even get why people call 
this the impossible game.

Guess the game is driving 
me crazy at some times.

Yes! Yes! Yes!
Yes, I'm doing good.
How do you get past that?

How are you supposed 
to actually get past it?
If it's hard to go underneath...

I can do this.
I can do this.

I'm trying to jump over 
these obstacles and not get killed,

It's one of those games 
where it feels so simple,
I knew that was gonna happen.
If only there were check points.
I've never gotten to that part.

It's a bit like Flappy Bird in a sense
because you have to think on the spot.

This really helps with your thinking,
if you think about it,

'cause of how much 
you have to use your brain.

It feels like the game is mocking me
because it keeps playing
the same music each time I do this.
This game is breaking my mind up.

Like, the best games are the ones 
that can make you feel emotion:
I feel so proud of myself.

I like that everything's 
made out of shapes.
I bet that's why it's called Geometry Dash.

Here we go.
Here we go.

Come on! Come on! Come on!
Come on! Come on!

I've already done 40 tries?
You gotta be kidding me.
Bam, bam, bam, bam, bam, bam.

Only that much more
and then I would've beat it.
I can beat this level and tell everyone.
I think I got my high score!

I haven't beat my high score 
on my iPad though.
If I beat this, I beat the whole level!
I proved to myself I'm still that good!

Stereo madness is beaten!
Eat on that, level!

Thanks for watching us play 
Geometry Dash on the React channel.

Comment what game 
you want us to play next.
I think actual Geometry is better than this.
